edu.CSUSM.testTaker.Backend

Interface Registerable

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Course, CourseProgress, Question, Test

    public interface Registerable
    An interface for all objects that can be stored in LibraryController. Operations that can be done on an object in the library regardless of what it is belong here.
    Author:
    StevenC
